Notes: NCAA Division III section semifinal... SP will play Pacific Lutheran Saturday
at 7 pm... WU led 48-46 with 11:58 left when Spann picked up fourth foul and
SP went on 10-2 run... SP ties school record for wins in a season set in 1987.
Loss snaps WU's 18 game win streak... Crowd of 1762 is a sellout.
Game.Officials: Mike Bronson,  Anne Nehring,  Stacy Jameson
